      "role": "user",
      "content": "I am a member of the local school board and we are currently drafting a new policy regarding student cell phone use in the classroom. We need to find a balance between allowing students to have phones for safety/emergency contact and minimizing the distractions they cause during instructional time. Could you provide a formal draft of a cell phone policy for us to review? It should include sections for permitted use, prohibited use, and consequences for violations.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
